{"tid":1982970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一圖解釋油的供求格價","createTime":"2020-04-21T13:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T15:16:09.000Z","uid":338879,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"599350ada653694aade5cc706a83663670aace62","tid":1982970,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RppNZae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRppNZae.jpg&h=f47e59c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">粉紅色線＝supply curve</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">藍色線 ＝demand curve</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來supply demand 的 equilibrium 位係A點，格價較高<br />\n<br />\n後來經濟收皮，無人買油，demand curve 斜度下降，而就算OPEC減幾多產都冇用，即管supply curve向左移，但個新的equilibrium 位已經去左B點，價格始終都係低<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">結論：一日經濟運行無好返，唔好幻想油價可以實質企穩上返（短炒幾蚊就另計喇）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟唔係major econ, 只係借supply demand curve吹下，econ 高手歡迎指正"},{"pid":"7aca2dcf0ac7fd8220a5db59e4ad1d2be0ccf463","tid":1982970,"uid":23931,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"抽象派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719879cb4fa6e14a11d361cb1b793734c5431121","tid":1982970,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03c84ebd2918a6677167b2183fa3e637c217c21","tid":1982970,"uid":152714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"點解 油價會咁影響個股市？<br />\n銀行 借咗好多錢比掘油公司？"},{"pid":"ff3e6530d1f3e6a0d38921b926c707dfcb4f57f4","tid":1982970,"uid":55189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2