人買油，demand curve 斜度下降，而就算OPEC減幾多產都冇用，即管supply curve向左移，但個新的equilibrium 位已經去左B點，價格始終都係低<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">結論：一日經濟運行無好返，唔好幻想油價可以實質企穩上返（短炒幾蚊就另計喇）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟唔係major econ, 只係借supply demand curve吹下，econ 高手歡迎指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"Supply curve ok不過呢個好似係shift in demand (成條curve郁) instead of change in elasticity?"},{"pid":"5a9f6cb1ee8681371f98ee208eea75ec9b09d0c7","tid":1982970,"uid":124584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"On9 關 demand elasticity 咩事 d跌成條左移架 你話有能源取代石油就話關elasticity 事唧 同埋就算當你假設啱（根本錯晒concept) 只要s減到去一定數量 個價一定可以等如或高於舊價 中一開始重新學過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adc68aaf2ce0711f1d9b72a67311fbe9fe2133f","tid":1982970,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"422ff48d04f34efb6af466d21adb5125865ae46a","tid":1982970,"uid":252864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"599350ada653694aade5cc706a83663670aace62","tid":1982970,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RppNZae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRppNZae.jpg&h=f47e59c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">粉紅色線＝supply curve</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">藍色線 ＝demand curve</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來supply demand 的 equilibrium 位係A點，格價較高<br />\n<br />\n後來經濟收皮，無人買油，demand curve 斜度下降，而就算OPEC減幾多產都冇用，即管supply curve向左移，但個新的equilibrium 位已經去左B點，價格始終都係低<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">結論：一日經濟運行無好返，唔好幻想油價可以實質企穩上返（短炒幾蚊就另計喇）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟唔係major econ, 只係借supply demand curve吹下，econ 高手歡迎指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"Supply curve ok不過呢個好似係shift in demand (成條curve郁) instead of change in elasticity?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"又好似係<img s